{"tid":1698894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸央行擬現金管理　深圳私人提存20萬人民幣須登記","createTime":"2019-11-07T23:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T17:26:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a3f367e7d3d40cd08307e5e6111a86660be899","tid":1698894,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:15:15.000Z","msg":"央行擬現金管理 深圳私人提存20萬人民幣須登記<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191106/bkn-20191106172838961-1106_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191106%2Fbkn-20191106172838961-1106_00952_001.html&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=5085bc2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191106/bkn-20191106172838961-1106_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行周二（5日）宣布，為推動大額現金管理工作，防止腐敗、偷逃稅、洗錢等違法問題，近日起草《中國人民銀行關於在河北省、浙江省、深圳市試點開展大額現金管理的通知（公開徵求意見稿）》，擬在上述3地展開為期2年的大額現金管理，客戶提取或存入指定金額以上的現金時，必須事先登記。民眾可在下月5日前提出意見。<br />\n<br />\n三地的單位帳戶管理的起點金額均為50萬元（人民幣‧下同，約57萬港元），對個人帳戶管理金額起點分別是河北省10萬元（約11.4萬港元）、浙江省30萬元（約34萬港元）、深圳市20萬元（約22.8萬港元）。新規例先在河北試點實施，然後在浙江和深圳推廣全面規範商業銀行大額現金業務。其中，深圳會探索個人帳戶大額現金管理、加強監測出入境及香港地區人民幣現金業務情況，選擇適宜地市探索推動個人收入報告措施。<br />\n<br />\n央行指，近年非現金支付發展迅速，但現金需求有增無減，尤其是大額現金廣泛使用，容易被各類型違法犯罪活動利用，蘊含較大風險。中國對大額現金管理的監管覆蓋面有限、法律效力不足。新規例設定的金額，高於社會大眾正常的使用量，故不會造成任何不便。"},{"pid":"635b4746d22a3a8c8506e9cc11723624bc0d915f","tid":1698894,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21309d3b68632f69b4996122aed300ad4f73f01","tid":1698894,"uid":50457,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:24:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">民眾可在下月5日前提出意見。</span><br />\n<br />\n中共都仲有假咨詢一個月，逃犯條例係無咨詢市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f51580ab7907e0c5cdf00b81eb1b31cf5f74a4e","tid":1698894,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4898ab337b2df18601d01e413ee20c0eaf2cdb21","tid":1698894,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:05:27.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係即時生效就大撚獲 排到返黎香港"},{"pid":"603348882759c6f8e3a669ecff233f01d22d2b7a","tid":1698894,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國領導人真係好，處處都為民著想。前一排先照顧青少年防沈迷打機，而家又照顧大眾財產安全。中國係一個安全又先進嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df6cb249e31a0443bc1c4848ad6d1bec302f7b4","tid":1698894,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:22:19.000Z","msg":"打擊地下錢莊走資"},{"pid":"946e57e07b487d106b880e7b5f4d028fa954d4f0","tid":1698894,"uid":218648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"海外評論人士文小剛認為，中共此舉和現在大陸一些地區民眾到銀行擠兌有關，中共害怕民眾的擠兌蔓延，其實在中國，中共要想知道誰取了大額存款，到銀行一查就明白了，搞這個登記就是為了恐嚇民眾，警告你們誰去銀行取錢共產黨都知道。另外就是中共資金吃緊，它希望民眾把錢留在銀行。<br />\n<br />\n日前，繼洛陽伊川農商銀行出現擠兌取錢現象僅一週，遼寧省營口市沿海銀行也發生大批儲戶前往銀行取錢的擠兌風波。11月6日晚間，當地警方稱拘留了9人，指控其「發布不實言論」。"},{"pid":"de6efc301dc4aeba343d0f36c40891fd7d033ebe","tid":1698894,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:51:37.000Z","msg":"佢哋都大把方法啦"},{"pid":"ddf676d3fea40cc3b0405ac874a77bea78536ee4","tid":1698894,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a86ad9791d66035bfc40bb57f06d0ca5e426ebc","tid":1698894,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔用cash ga咩"},{"pid":"a8cbe252ba0039630ee7dc0ade9dd305ac463565","tid":1698894,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"熱烈慶祝支爆等左廿年終於見證到"},{"pid":"d19ed769dc270b98a46f096b6b7d6c5fc5c45b41","tid":1698894,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"近年非現金支付發展迅速，但現金需求有增無減，尤其是大額現金廣泛使用<br />\n<br />\n中國式邏輯，就係自相矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff4b80daa1fdbedd064fe4df5c769841dfba8f4","tid":1698894,"uid":271851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}